and displacement for a given time interval are all proportional. Thus the
bulk viscosity of the fluid in Laplace space, η ̃(s) with Laplace frequency s,
relates to the microscopic memory function by a constant of proportionality
ζ ̃(s) = 6πaη ̃(s), (2.12)
