This is known to microrheologists as the generalised Stokes-Einstein rela
tion (GSER) and is seminal in the study of diffusion to understand the
mechanics of viscoelastic materials. Interpretation of the MSD is further
aided by the equivalence of MSD and creep compliance in a step-stress
experiment[113].
