the subscript. For 2.5 ➭m-radius sphere in water, held with trap stiffness
κ =0.1 pN/➭m, the trap relaxation sets the low-frequency limit of the band
width to 2 Hz.
Here I have neglected the Fax ́en’s law correction to translational viscosity[145],
